snippet.title: Tricky Super Mario Bros. U - 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Tricky Super Mario Bros. U is a mod of New Super Mario Bros. U that aims to twist the familiar into something new for players looking for some extra challenge. This mod will contain a mix of revamped NSMBU levels and original stages for Mario to travel through as he tries to escape the never-ending nightmare that Bowser has trapped him in.

The music in this trailer is an original composition by @brickblock369
There is currently no set release date for the mod, but you can find an outdated demo of World 1 here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1EF01KAsACwh0aGYuTAEjpY6dRCrbnuU7/view

For more information on New Super Mario Bros. U (and Wii) modding, be sure to check out the Evolution Discord server: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ
